race.description: Welcome To Night Racing In Launnie Plate (C1)
race.comment: OPENSEA (2) brings a 4.5 Maiden win from the synthetic this distance and Darmanin stays aboard. On a 5-day return and it won't surprise if he goes on with the job. DON'T GIVE UP (1) peaks off a 1L defeat on the synthetic this trip and grade. He was good at Hobart prior and won't get so far off them here. Loses Darmanin but is a big threat. TIZSA NICE DROP (7) is another easy synthetic Maiden winner back to the turf. Maps well and she can't be ruled out. HARRATA (6) dropped back miles to a sprint on the synthetic and disappointed as a short-priced favourite. Better at a mile and the 4kg claim brings him into it.
